{
  "stem": "26609.11",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The prison had the name of the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Laskiego.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And was very well-known prison, mostly for political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was a lot, then-- mostly the wives of the Russian officers who left with the army and they left behind their wives.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't take-- because they were in a hurry to get out, because the Germans were from the West Poland, coming forward.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they're in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They fled and left the wife behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Germans wanted to find out about their wives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They interrogated them about the Russian officers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they didn't tell them anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said that, in their gardens and their homes, they hid some war [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] documents or whatever they searched for.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They couldn't tell them anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they imprisoned them there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beginning of '43.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the middle of winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- no, that was end of '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, '42.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me from the street-- I told you before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had no idea what will happen in the prison or what happened to my family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, as I said before, my parents were in Grodek, not in Lwow-- and my youngest brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of the sisters was at the hospital in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they killed all the inmates of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I found out later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was not in contact with anybody with the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she, from Lublin, was deported, I don't know exactly, from the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think from the street she was deported to Germany for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That must happened before, but I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She told me later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She left the ghetto, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
